{
  "stem": "22734.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was not very much leisure time, because I had a terribly strict mother and she-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and she-- she saw to it that I don't have too much leisure time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had this governess who was-- who was strict, but she was basically very nice, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even though she was German, she didn't do me any harm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then in nine-- she was from the Sudetenland, which was, after Munich, annexed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she had, I remember, such idiocies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Her brother was an architect in-- in one of the border towns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she had a little nephew, and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of whom she was very fond.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she had a sister, and this sister became a nun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they went to her ordainment, we would call it, or whatever you call it, in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she described the ceremony so vividly that I couldn't sleep for a month.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then after, she was with us already in the first address.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she taught me German, and French, and piano.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she went to the park with me we-- when I was little.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So in the afternoon, after homework and German and piano, we went to the par-- to the park.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Or in winter, we-- first, we went to the park.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were not bad winters, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Sort of nasty, wet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But in the park, I played with all the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then we came home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then it was, again, German, French, and piano.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then was supper and-- and bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what do I do now?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
